{"tid":877350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬化騰上網求教比人串係缺乏實際經驗的大學生","createTime":"2018-10-26T09:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T12:02:57.000Z","uid":28765,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6e233312870297b9e149b0e00604dbbe137fe5ce","tid":877350,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:33:53.000Z","msg":"10 月 24 日凌晨，在知乎平台上認證為「騰訊公司董事會主席兼首席執行官」的名為 ponyma 的用戶，提出了一個問題：未來十年哪些基礎科學突破會影響互聯網科技產業？產業互聯網和消費互聯網融合創新，會帶來哪些改變？<br />\n無論是知乎所認證的頭銜本身，還是 ponyma 的命名指向，都毫無疑問地指向人們心中的互聯網大佬&mdash;&mdash;馬化騰。而面對大佬的現身提問，大家更是紛紛踴躍地建言獻策&mdash;&mdash;一時間讓人聯想起七年前騰訊在追求變革之際開展的「診斷騰訊」的研討會。<br />\n<br />\n不過，可能大家想得有點多了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.leiphone.com/uploads/new/images/20181024/5bd03a6ef2506.jpg?imageView2/2/w/740\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.leiphone.com%2Fuploads%2Fnew%2Fimages%2F20181024%2F5bd03a6ef2506.jpg%3FimageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F740&h=a7ee73f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hksilicon.com/articles/1691667\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hksilicon.com%2Farticles%2F1691667&d=pBvlUjHteML23fzRuHOJCm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=383e498f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hksilicon.com/articles/1691667</a>"},{"pid":"4db4297ab0431c16e11875ef8a5caf5144148357","tid":877350,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42cf1357173b5de5c3dfb5beb3349a49331818aa","tid":877350,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4db4297ab0431c16e11875ef8a5caf5144148357","tid":877350,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:21:11.000Z","msg":"出現鳥~<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b468155999872fff954